seo: Intellian Aptus Web,操作系统命令注入漏洞,远程攻击,任意命令执行
seo_en: Intellian Aptus Web, OS command injection vulnerability, remote attack, arbitrary command execution
summary: 检测Intellian Aptus Web 1.24版本中的操作系统命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可利用该漏洞通过JSON数据中的Q字段执行任意操作系统命令。
summary_en: Detect the OS command injection vulnerability in Intellian Aptus Web 1.24 version. Remote attackers can exploit this vulnerability to execute arbitrary OS commands via the Q field in JSON data.
